Package com.sun.tools.visualvm.tools.jvmstat

Jvmstat support in VisualVM.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
JvmstatListener Interface for listeners of JvmstatModel changes.
 

Class Summary
JvmJvmstatModel This class encapsulates information available via Jvmstat counters.
JvmJvmstatModelFactory The JvmJvmstatModelFactory class is a factory class for getting the JvmJvmstatModel representation for the Application.
JvmstatModel This class uses Jvmstat technology (http://java.sun.com/performance/jvmstat/) to obtatin various information from JVM.
JvmstatModelFactory The JvmstatModelFactory class is a factory class for getting the JvmstatModel representation for the Application.
MonitoredValue This class encapsulates a counter exported via Jvmstat
